name: Let's Go Left
Text: 'Non-pilot characters aboard starships are forfeit -4. Whenever a player''s starship is ''hit'', that player loses 1 Force (2 if starship was hit by Proton Torpedoes). At systems where you have only [Republic] starships, all of those starships are immune to attrition < 4. At sites related to a system you occupy, your battle destinies may not be canceled by opponent.',
